// WWE Smackdown! Vs. Raw 2011 (NTSC-U)
// File generated by GameHacking.org

[Add Non-Playable Characters to Selection Screen\Add Hornswoggle]
author=BigBossman
description=Most of these characters can only be played if they are a manager. Its possible to play using them as a wrestler, but it isn't easy. If you go to the random icon ("?"), it will potentially choose an NPC for you. They are also easily selectable during the Royal Rumble. Just select "Change Participants" & select the NPCs you want to be in the Royal Rumble. They don't have an entrance, theme music, abilities, enemies, or allies, but that can be adjusted. Their attributes will have low ratings, but since they will be added to the Manage Superstar List, you can adjust their attributes using the "Enables Superstar Attribute Editing" code.
patch=1,EE,006C2729,extended,00000001

