[Match Rules Modifiers\Escape Through the Cage Door Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This only works in a Steel Cage Match. When on, it will allow you to win a Steel Cage Match by escaping through the door. This also works with Steel Cage Matches that have more than two players.
Values - 
00 - Escape Through the Cage Door Always Off
01 - Escape Through the Cage Door Always On 
patch=1,EE,006BC73C,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Extreme Rules Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=When this is activated, it will bring up the weapon selection wheel when you try to pull a weapon out from under the ring.
Values – 
00 – Extreme Rules are Always Off
01 – Extreme Rules Always On
patch=1,EE,006BC748,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,00000000,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Finisher Match Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Allows you to win by performing your finisher on an opponent. Once its performed, it will show that they are KOed.
Values – 
00 – Finisher Matches are Off
01 – Finisher Matches are On
patch=1,EE,006BC727,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\First Blood Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Allows you to win by making your opponent bleed.
Values – 
00 – First Blood is Always Off
01 – First Blood is Always On
patch=1,EE,006BC738,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Flaming Table Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=When enabled, this will allow you to set a table on fire & win by putting your opponent through it. Best used with a match that has tables such as a Table Match or TLC Match.
Values - 
00 - Flaming Table Match Always Off
01 - Flaming Table Match Always On 
patch=1,EE,006BC737,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Hardcore Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Before the WWE games had Extreme Rules Matches, they had Hardcore Rules where weapons were laying around outside the ring. When activated, there will be a sledge hammer & a steel chair laying outside the ring.
Values – 
00 – Hardcore is Off
01 – Hardcore is On
patch=1,EE,006BC721,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Hell In A Cell Match Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Causes the Hell In A Cell match to always be active or always inactive. If Might freeze up if activated with certain match types. 
Values - 
00 - Hell In A Cell Match Always Off
01 - Hell In A Cell Match Always On 
patch=1,EE,006BC724,extended,00000000

[Match Rules Modifiers\Inferno Match Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Allows flames to surround the ring with more than two players in a match, but you can't exit the ring. 
Values - 
00 - Inferno Match Always Off
01 - Inferno Match Always On
patch=1,EE,006BC74B,extended,00000000

