[Player 1 Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=These codes will enable you to play as any character within the game. This includes characters that are not normally selectable such as Hornswoggle, Paul Bearer, Hurricane, Referee, Michael Cole, Stephanie McMahon, Tiffany, ETC. You can even enable matches between men vs. women using these codes. Just be sure that you have DQs turned off or else, the male character will get disqualified. You can even have women fight in certain match types that they normally can't compete in. "CAW" is abbreviation for "Create-A-Wrestler".
