[Match Rules Modifiers\Required Number of Wins Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=In the Match Creator, there's an option for Best Two Out of Three Falls. When modified, this will determine the number of wins by Pinfall, Submission, Disqualification, Knockout, or Count Out needed to win the match. When there are more than two players in a match, this will work for them too.
patch=1,EE,006BC71D,extended,00000000

