[Match Rules Modifiers\TLC Match Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This is similar to the Ladder match except that is also allows you to pull tables out from under the ring. Tends to slow down gameplay when used on a 6-man tag team match & makes it to where the ladders can't be used.
Values - 
00 - TLC Match Always Off
01 - TLC Match Always On
patch=1,EE,006BC71C,extended,00000000

